INSTALL

	0. install SL4A
	1. download Android CLI executable from http://rebolsource.net/; rename it "rebol3"; place it in /sdcard/
	2. copy sl4a.reb, altjson.reb from this repo to /sdcard/
	3. copy rebol3.sh from this repo to /sdcard/sl4a/scripts/
	4. from SL4A launch rebol3.sh in terminal mode
	5. test: >> sl4a 'makeToast "Rebol is alive!"
	6. delete rebol3, altjson.reb, sl4a.reb from /sdcard/

SYNTAX

	sl4a method params

	method: lit-word! | string!

	params: block! or shortcut:

	shortcut:
		none => []
		value => [value]

	e.g. :

	sl4a 'getClipboard none
	sl4a 'setClipboard "Rebol"
	sl4a 'fullShow [layout-string title]
	sl4a 'fullDismiss none
	sl4a 'ttsSpeak "The voice of Rebol"


		

